---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout
	title="Punto Limpio"
	description="Información sobre el Punto Limpio de Cantillana: horarios, ubicación y residuos aceptados."
>
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="relative bg-primary overflow-hidden pt-36 pb-24 sm:pt-44 sm:pb-32 -mt-2">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10">
			<div
				class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary bg-white/10 mb-8 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm animate-fade"
			>
				Gestión de Residuos
			</div>
			<h1
				class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-6xl mb-8 leading-tight"
			>
				Punto Limpio de <span class="text-secondary">Cantillana</span>
			</h1>
			<p
				class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-lg opacity-90 text-slate-100 mb-10 leading-relaxed"
			>
				Instalación municipal destinada a la recogida selectiva de residuos domésticos 
				que no deben depositarse en los contenedores habituales.
			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
				<a
					href="#informacion"
					class="bg-secondary text-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold shadow-xl shadow-secondary/20 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all"
					>Ver Horarios y Ubicación</a
				>
				<a
					href="/"
					class="bg-white/10 text-white border border-white/20 backdrop-blur-md px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-white/20 transition-all"
					>Volver al Inicio</a
				>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- Decorative blobs -->
		<div
			class="absolute -top-24 -left-20 w-96 h-96 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"
		>
		</div>
		<div
			class="absolute -bottom-24 -right-20 w-96 h-96 bg-primary-light/30 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"
		>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Content Section -->
	<section id="informacion" class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
			
			<!-- Left Column: Info Cards -->
			<div class="space-y-8">
				<!-- Schedule Card -->
				<div class="glass-panel p-8 border-l-4 border-l-secondary">
					<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
						<div class="bg-secondary/20 p-3 rounded-xl text-secondary">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">Horarios</h2>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-4 text-slate-600">
						<div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">
							<span class="font-medium">Lunes a Viernes</span>
							<span class="text-primary font-bold">09:00 - 13:00 y 15:30 - 18:30</span>
						</div>
						<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
							<span class="font-medium">Sábados</span>
							<span class="text-primary font-bold">09:00 - 14:00</span>
						</div>
						<p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-4 italic">
							* Horario actualizado a marzo de 2026. Puede variar según la temporada (invierno/verano).
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Location Card -->
				<div class="glass-panel p-8 border-l-4 border-l-primary">
					<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
						<div class="bg-primary/10 p-3 rounded-xl text-primary">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">Ubicación</h2>
					</div>
					<p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
						C/ Alfareros esq. C/ Carboneros<br/>
						Polígono Industrial San Sebastián<br/>
						Cantillana, Sevilla.
					</p>
					<div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-xl h-48 w-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 overflow-hidden relative group">
                        <!-- Placeholder for map - in a real app would be an iframe or dynamic map -->
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1526778548025-fa2f459cd5c1?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Mapa" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-50 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" />
                        <span class="relative z-10 font-bold bg-white/80 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">Ver en Google Maps</span>
                        <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/Punto+Limpio+Cantillana+Alfareros" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="absolute inset-0 z-20"></a>
                    </div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Right Column: Rules & Info -->
			<div class="space-y-8">
				<div class="glass-panel p-8">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="text-secondary">●</span> ¿Qué puedes traer?
                    </h3>
					<ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-slate-600">
							<span class="text-secondary mt-1">✓</span> Muebles y enseres
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-slate-600">
							<span class="text-secondary mt-1">✓</span> Electrodomésticos
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-slate-600">
							<span class="text-secondary mt-1">✓</span> Escombros de obras menores
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-slate-600">
							<span class="text-secondary mt-1">✓</span> Pinturas y disolventes
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-slate-600">
							<span class="text-secondary mt-1">✓</span> Aceites usados
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-slate-600">
							<span class="text-secondary mt-1">✓</span> Pilas y baterías
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

                <div class="bg-amber-50 border-2 border-amber-100 rounded-2xl p-8 relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-amber-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
                            </svg>
                            Detalles Importantes
                        </h3>
                        <div class="space-y-4 text-amber-800/80">
                            <p>
                                <strong class="text-amber-900">Uso obligatorio:</strong> Es obligatorio clasificar los residuos y depositarlos en los contenedores correspondientes siguiendo las indicaciones del personal.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                <strong class="text-amber-900">Prohibición:</strong> Está totalmente prohibido depositar basuras o muebles en la vía pública o en la puerta del punto limpio fuera del horario establecido.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute -right-8 -bottom-8 text-amber-100 opacity-50 transform rotate-12">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-32 w-32" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 7l-.867 12.142A2 2 0 0116.138 21H7.862a2 2 0 01-1.995-1.858L5 7m5 4v6m4-6v6m1-10V4a1 1 0 00-1-1h-4a1 1 0 00-1 1v3M4 7h16" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="text-center p-6 bg-slate-100 rounded-2xl text-slate-500 text-sm">
                    <p>Gestionado por la <a href="https://lavegamancomunidad.es" class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline">Mancomunidad de Servicios La Vega</a>.</p>
                    <p class="mt-2">Teléfono de atención: <a href="tel:955111140" class="font-bold">955 11 11 40</a></p>
                </div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
